There are eight complaints of United India, with respect to public insurance.

00:03:24.519 --> 00:03:27.480
But, they got rejected because their ICR is higher.

00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:31.821
You will find the total incurred claims ratio of 83% in terms of Bajaj Allianz decent.

00:03:31.846 --> 00:03:34.626
